data.description: Seller will consider all reasonable offers! Nestled in the heart of Corsicana, TX, this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home offers 2049 sq. ft. of modern comfort. Recently painted with new vinyl flooring throughout, the interior exudes a crisp, inviting atmosphere. The living room at the front and spacious den at the back, complete with a brick fireplace, provide versatile living spaces. The kitchen, with its original cabinets newly painted, exudes warmth and functionality. A 2-car carport and covered driveway serve as a welcoming porch. Two storage buildings, a fenced yard, and a sunroom add practicality. The primary bedroom features an ensuite half bath for added convenience. The foundation was repaired in August 2022.  Eligible for FHA, VA, or conventional financing, this home is a true gem in Corsicana. Built in 1968, it combines modern updates with timeless charm. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!  This home has great investment potential as well. Schedule a tour today.
